== Overview ==
The standard 20mm Automatic Cannon fires bursts of high velocity rounds causing significant damage to unshielded, lightly armored targets.

== Where to Acquire ==
The 20mm Auto Cannon can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
